Package: kniterati
Type: Package
Title: Purl Rmd Source Code For Your R Package 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eric Kernfeld
Maintainer: Eric Kernfeld <eric.kern13@gmail.com>
Description: I write all my R packages in R markdown documents -- not just the vignettes, but the
    source as well. The R files are just there for the machine. This package can be run to 
    refresh the R files before running `devtools::install`.
License: MIT license
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
